1952;;Made in Heaven;;British;;John Paddy Carstairs;;David Tomlinson, Petula Clark;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Made_in_Heaven_(1952_film);;Young married couple Basil (David Tomlinson) and Julie Topham (Petula Clark) enter the ancient annual Dummow Flitch Trials (in which a married couple can win a side of bacon if at the end of one year, they have 'not wisht themselves unmarried again'). However, the Topham's happy household, and then an entire village is thrown into chaos with the arrival of an attractive Hungarian housemaid (Sonja Ziemann).